title: "Squares" by Wall-dec
description: Comes in square sheets (14 inches square) ready for hanging. Includes twelve different patterns, each shown in four different colorways. The designs include: Yorktown, Strato, Salem, Anchors A-Weigh, Jamestown, On Parade, Haworth, Ribbons, Nantucket, Concord and Shadow Leaves. There is a dated price list inside the front and back covers.
